  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/e2f546e49ab1baad6eceb1bba0303316.avif?t=1769194358\" width=612 height=163 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/384845b9c6ab5b55387bc241f2b800a7.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️ <strong>Scout</strong> procedural lands that shift beneath your feet. <br>🗡️ <strong>Survive</strong> against the fierce barbarian horde. <br>🎆 <strong>Discover</strong> deep systems and powerful combos. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/5309f24a0c121489d1cfc2927f694fda.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧪 <strong>Mix</strong> over 200 game-changing technologies. <br>🎲 <strong>Improvise</strong> to make the most of each unique run. <br>❄️ <strong>Watch</strong> your choices snowball, creating wildly different civilizations. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/977526fd110747c9e134ba373fcdb361.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎴 <strong>Draft</strong> your perfect deck of cards to craft a unique strategy. <br>🔨 <strong>Upgrade</strong> your cards, units and cities in every era. <br>📈 <strong>Build</strong> an enduring empire, from the stone age to the singularity.  <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/dc300d9f7b95785063da9d165f4e4531.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>Achieve</strong> tough challenges to reveal new content. <br>✨ <strong>Unlock</strong> permanent upgrades between matches. <br>⚰️ <strong>Die</strong> in spectacular fashion, and try again! </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/e2f546e49ab1baad6eceb1bba0303316.avif?t=1769194358\" width=612 height=163 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/384845b9c6ab5b55387bc241f2b800a7.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️ <strong>Scout</strong> procedural lands that shift beneath your feet. <br>🗡️ <strong>Survive</strong> against the fierce barbarian horde. <br>🎆 <strong>Discover</strong> deep systems and powerful combos. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/5309f24a0c121489d1cfc2927f694fda.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧪 <strong>Mix</strong> over 200 game-changing technologies. <br>🎲 <strong>Improvise</strong> to make the most of each unique run. <br>❄️ <strong>Watch</strong> your choices snowball, creating wildly different civilizations. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/977526fd110747c9e134ba373fcdb361.webp?t=1769194358\" width=277 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎴 <strong>Draft</strong> your perfect deck of cards to craft a unique strategy. <br>🔨 <strong>Upgrade</strong> your cards, units and cities in every era. <br>📈 <strong>Build</strong> an enduring empire, from the stone age to the singularity.  <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275940/extras/dc300d9f7b95785063da9d165f4e4531